# AvokAI eval / build artifacts
# v2_index_state.json is rebuild state (which laws are embedded in default_v2).
# It churns on every `make build-v2` and shouldn't be in git. Eval result
# snapshots in tests/eval/results/eval_*.json ARE committed because the docs
# reference them by filename.
tests/eval/results/v2_index_state.json
